The Mother Goddess is a figure of ancient Sardinian archaeology. 
She was considered to be the one with the capability to transmit life, since people believed that the survival of human race depended solely on the women, spreading vital energy that males just didn't own.

My aim is to represent a granitic shape, bound to the eart, strong and unfailing against turns of fate, 
that protects a precious heart that shimmers like a ruby.

A concept proposal submitted for the contest @_gentiles_ launched in search for the cover of SOLO A META', their upcoming single, hoping it matches their needs!
